reviewText: All of the WWE's sexiest females head to Mexico for the 2004 photo shoot. It's eye candy galore as Trish Stratus, Stacy Keibler, Torrie Wilson, Sable, Lita, Dawn Marie, Victoria, Ivory, Nidia, Miss Jackie, Molly, Gail Kim, Jacqueline, and Jazz pose for provactive photographs while commenting on the importance of this magazine on their careers. If you're expecting anything more than a bunch of gorgeous ladies posing in bikinis on the beach then save your money.
Title: WWE: Divas - South of the Border

Title: WWE: Divas - South of the Border

reviewText: The WWE Divas head down south of the border to mexico for the 2004 Divas Magazine Shoot. The divas particpated were Victoria, Ivory, Trish Stratus, Molly Holly, Gail Kim, Jazz, Jacqueline, Stacy Keibler, Lita, Miss Jackie, Torrie Wilson, Dawn Marie, Sable and Nidia. This DVD should be packed with extras for you which may contain Lita's return (Molly Holly & Gail Kim vs. Trish Stratus) Miss Jackie & Stacy Keibler uniting (Rico with Miss Jackie vs. Rob Conway with Renee Dupree) or Sables return (Torrie Wilson's Playboy Celebration). Also interviews with Torrie Wilson, Stacy Keibler and Sable from Confidential, Exclusive Trish Cam and Hidden Extras.
Title: WWE: Divas - South of the Border

reviewText: Who cares about the photoshoots? i just wanted to see the wrestling matches but of course they are all 2 minutes. waste of time and money
Title: WWE: Divas - South of the Border

reviewText: When I first saw this I didn't think much of it, but now that it's 2012 and the divas division in WWE is in a downward spiral I took a look back at these dvds and thought, "Wow, the divas division was so awesome back then! What happened???"This has got the same 1 hour special that they did every year (at that time) but with lots and lots of extras. Bunch of great matches, escpescially Victoria vs. Lita in the first ever (and only) WWE Divas Steel Cage Match. Plus lots of features from WWE Confidential (another great show that sadly got the ax).
Title: WWE: Divas - South of the Border
